skdetail:
This skill contains: dynamic content.
Invocation Name: insight timer
des: Insight Timer is a simple timer tool that lets you set a timer for your meditation session (between 5 to 60 minutes) and plays a Tibetan bowl sound every ten minutes as a guide during your session. Start by saying "Alexa, open Insight Timer" and follow the prompts.
priv: The developer reported that this skill does not collect personal information.
